overview.en: KELLCHAIN is a decentralized blockchain game public chain jointly launched by the Cayman Islands KELL Foundation, which is jointly established by global entertainment game companies and innovative developers, digital asset management institutions, and financial institutions (including technology finance).
overview.zh: KELLCHAIN是由开Cayman Islands KELL Foundation发起，联合全球娱乐游戏企业和创新 开发者、数字资产管理机构、金融机构（含科技金融）共同建设的去中心化区块链游戏公链。
